item.description:
Come break the Winter Blues
at the FIRST ANNUAL Spring Fling Party
with famous pagan singer Kellianna! :)

Saturday, March 5, 2011
at

The Knights of Columbus
110 South Main St.
Gardner, Mass

Pot Luck Dinner
6:00- 8:00 pm
(list to be sent out to group, there is a full kitchen at the venue)

Concert with Kellianna
8:00- 10:00

CASH BAR

Check out Kellianna's website at:

http://www.kellianna....


Pre-paid tickets Tickets are: $20.00 per person

Tickets will be available at Terrapin Traders- Gardner
and at Corner Stone Creations- Fiskdale By Jan 20th
They are also available with paypal through the meet up group,
and also checks can be sent to me-
please email me at: talawolf7@webtv.net
or talawitch@charter.net for my address :)

I am also looking for volunteers for a decorating party prior to the meet up
and a clean up crew. Please email me, or comment in your rsvp if you are interested in this :)
